# Conventional Commit Template
# https://www.conventionalcommits.org/
#
# Format:
# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# <body>
#
# <footer>
#
# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore
# Scope: ui, backend, worker, core, cli, docs, ci
# Subject: imperative, lowercase, no period at end
# Body: explain WHAT and WHY (not HOW)
# Footer: reference issues (Closes #123, Fixes #456)

# Example:
# feat(ui): add collapsible dock panels
#
# Implement QDockWidget-based layout with user-configurable
# dock positions and visibility toggles.
#
# Closes #42
